<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{subject}}</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #F5F7FA; color: #1a1a2e; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 16px; }
    .card { background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(13,71,161,0.08); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D47A1 0%, #00838F 100%); padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header img { height: 48px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .header h1 { color: #ffffff; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.3px; }
    .header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .body h2 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #0D47A1; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .body p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #374151; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .body strong { color: #0D47A1; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D47A1, #00838F); color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .info-box { background: #F0F7FF; border-left: 4px solid #00BCD4; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .info-box p { margin: 0; color: #0D47A1; font-size: 14px; }
    .warning-box { background: #FFF8E1; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .warning-box p { margin: 0; color: #92400E; font-size: 14px; }
    .danger-box { background: #FEF2F2; border-left: 4px solid #EF4444; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .danger-box p { margin: 0; color: #991B1B; font-size: 14px; }
    .success-box { background: #F0FDF4; border-left: 4px solid #22C55E; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .success-box p { margin: 0; color: #166534; font-size: 14px; }
    .divider { height: 1px; background: #E5E7EB; margin: 24px 0; }
    .table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0; }
    .table th { background: #F3F4F6; color: #6B7280; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 10px 14px; text-align: left; }
    .table td { padding: 12px 14px; font-size: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E7EB; color: #374151; }
    .table td strong { color: #111827; }
    .footer { background: #F9FAFB; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB; }
    .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #9CA3AF; line-height: 1.6; }
    .footer a { color: #0D47A1; text-decoration: none; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; background: #DCFCE7; color: #166534; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px; }
    .badge.warning { background: #FEF9C3; color: #854D0E; }
    .badge.danger { background: #FEE2E2; color: #991B1B; }
    .badge.info { background: #DBEAFE; color: #1E40AF; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>SANTAREX ERP</h1>
        <p>Gestion hospitalière intelligente — IBIG SOFT</p>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        {{{body}}}
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement par <strong>SANTAREX ERP</strong> — <a href="https://santarex.ibigsoft.com">santarex.ibigsoft.com</a><br/>
          IBIG SOFT | <a href="mailto:contact@ibigsoft.com">contact@ibigsoft.com</a> | +225 27 22 27 60 14<br/>
          <a href="https://ibigsoft.com">ibigsoft.com</a> — Abidjan, Côte d'Ivoire
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
